    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_comical-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_achieve-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様です、mihoさん",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば、この前買った車ですけど\n仕事先に行くのに、使ってらっしゃるんですね",
      "startTime": 5.645456044,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_03-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "せっかく買ったのですから、乗るに決まってるでしょう\nやっと一人で静かに移動出来るようになったのですし",
      "startTime": 13.1781855185,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_03-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ……本体価格は確かに安かったですけど\nいかんせん古い車でしたから、総点検が必要になって",
      "startTime": 21.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_03-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "古いパーツと、マフラーを静かな物に換えてもらったら\n結局、高くつきましたけどね",
      "startTime": 30.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "中古車あるあるですねぇ\nでも、ちゃんと手を掛けて大事にしているんですね",
      "startTime": 35.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_03-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "当然です。……それにあの、暴走族じみた外装も\n別に、悪いことばかりではないですし",
      "startTime": 45.3900772072,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんですか！？",
      "startTime": 47.8480259816,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_03-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "まず煽られることはありませんし\n周りから車間距離を取ってくれるので、快適ですね",
      "startTime": 52.1180259863,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "な、なるほど。……ところで、あの車について\nちょっとご相談……お願いしたいことがあるんですが",
      "startTime": 59.5981354341,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_03-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "……なんでしょう",
      "startTime": 64.5536491552,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "その、mihoさんの車を\n俺に運転させてもらうことは、出来ませんか？",
      "startTime": 68.7634788305,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（それから少し後、年明け早々に）\n（スリクスは新曲のMVを撮影することになった）",
      "startTime": 77.5999982198,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_03-mhk007.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……やっと着きましたね\nまったく、衣装を着たまま移動することになるなんて",
      "startTime": 85.3333315532,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "すみません、スタイリストさんの都合で\nどうしても、スタジオまで来ていただくのが難しく……",
      "startTime": 92.6625329219,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_03-mhk008.m4a",
      "text": "怠慢の言い訳は結構\n難しくても手配するのが、マネージャーの仕事でしょう",
      "startTime": 98.7333315532,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_03-mhk009.m4a",
      "text": "お陰で、せっかく買った私の車に貴方を乗せて\nあまつさえ、運転させる羽目になったんですから",
      "startTime": 106.5999966939,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "す、すみません！　でもmihoさんの車なら\nかさばる衣装でも、三人一度にスタジオに運べますし",
      "startTime": 113.4666633606,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "衣装のままmihoさんに運転してもらうのは\n動き辛くて、万が一と言うことがありますから",
      "startTime": 120.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_03-mhk010.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……分かっていますよ\nただし、二度目はありませんからね",
      "startTime": 127.5999987285,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_03-mhk011.m4a",
      "text": "それにしても……さっきの貴方の運転\n暴走族仕様の車にあるまじき、安全運転でしたね",
      "startTime": 136.0666653951,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "交通事故は嫌ですからね。……特に、この時期には",
      "startTime": 139.8824923556,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_03-mhk012.m4a",
      "text": "……あぁ、交通事故と言ったら\nええ……私も、出来れば見たくはないですね",
      "startTime": 150.2666633606,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_03-mhk013.m4a",
      "text": "さて。それでは、撮影が始まるようなので",
      "startTime": 155.7743921796,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_03-mhk014.m4a",
      "text": "みなさん、あけましておめでとうございます\n新年最初の撮影、どうぞよろしくお願いしますね",
      "startTime": 165.9999936421,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "（はぁ……年末年始には、どうしても思い出すな）\n（あれから何度も正月が来たと、たまに信じられなくなる）",
      "startTime": 175.3333269755,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_03-mhk015.m4a",
      "text": "はい、初詣にはfranとkanaと行きましたよ\nいつも仲が良くて羨ましい？　ええ、それだけが自慢で",
      "startTime": 184.92194359,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_03-mhk016.m4a",
      "text": "でも残念ながら、振り袖ではなく普段着だったので\n衣装でも着物風のを着られるのは、嬉しいですね",
      "startTime": 195.5333300272,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_03-mhk017.m4a",
      "text": "こうして、お屠蘇もいただいていると\nますます、おめでたい気分に……ふふっ",
      "startTime": 202.2232322005,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_03-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "み、mihoさん！　撮影中にお酒は……\nましてや仕事先の人達もいる前で、お酒は……！",
      "startTime": 209.1386060273,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_03-mhk018.m4a",
      "text": "……はぁ？　すみません\nうちのマネージャーが何か勘違いしたみたいで",
      "startTime": 216.7333178201,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_10_03-mhk019.m4a",
      "text": "ほら、これはお酒じゃなくてただの水ですよ\n撮影用の小道具ですから、安心して下さい",
      "startTime": 223.6999844867,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4873.4387757000095,
          "startTime": 228.5734232624
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
